query:
SELECT
                    COALESCE(packets_received, 0) as "packets_received!: _",
                    COALESCE(packets_sent, 0) as "packets_sent!: _",
                    COALESCE(packets_dropped, 0) as "packets_dropped!: _"
                FROM nym_nodes_packet_stats_raw
                WHERE node_id = $1
                ORDER BY timestamp_utc DESC
                LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1
